Saffa v2.0.0.6

Saffa, a Hebrew Reference Guide, is an educational
tool to aid in the learning of the Hebrew language.
It is both a Hebrew document production tool, as
well as a resource for accessing grammatical
features of the language.  Its features are
useful for beginners and advanced students
alike.

For any question. Post here on this forum
or mail me.
